{"words":[{"word":"into","count":3},{"word":"td","count":3},{"word":"little","count":2},{"word":"leaf","count":2},{"word":"side","count":2},{"word":"sounds","count":2},{"word":"long","count":2},{"word":"use","count":2},{"word":"tunes","count":2},{"word":"leaves","count":2},{"word":"mourning","count":2},{"word":"aix","count":2},{"word":"attacked","count":2},{"word":"boy","count":2},{"word":"yep","count":2},{"word":"human","count":2},{"word":"things","count":2},{"word":"wrong","count":1},{"word":"kiddo","count":1},{"word":"rascal","count":1},{"word":"ahem","count":1},{"word":"old","count":1},{"word":"man","count":1},{"word":"strangers","count":1},{"word":"sure","count":1},{"word":"something","count":1},{"word":"uniquely","count":1},{"word":"popular","count":1},{"word":"among","count":1},{"word":"older","count":1},{"word":"generations","count":1},{"word":"ready","count":1},{"word":"ordinary","count":1},{"word":"shush","count":1},{"word":"away","count":1},{"word":"brat","count":1},{"word":"find","count":1},{"word":"pinch","count":1},{"word":"together","count":1},{"word":"hold","count":1},{"word":"close","count":1},{"word":"lips","count":1},{"word":"blow","count":1},{"word":"along","count":1},{"word":"edge","count":1},{"word":"change","count":1},{"word":"pitch","count":1},{"word":"indeed","count":1},{"word":"turn","count":1},{"word":"anything","count":1},{"word":"world","count":1},{"word":"instrument","count":1},{"word":"music","count":1},{"word":"put","count":1},{"word":"heart","count":1},{"word":"express","count":1},{"word":"feelings","count":1},{"word":"young","count":1},{"word":"sit","count":1},{"word":"cliff","count":1},{"word":"day","count":1},{"word":"work","count":1},{"word":"play","count":1},{"word":"simple","count":1},{"word":"bird","count":1},{"word":"rarely","count":1},{"word":"anyone","count":1},{"word":"watch","count":1},{"word":"two","count":1},{"word":"always","count":1},{"word":"flying","count":1},{"word":"beside","count":1},{"word":"distance","count":1},{"word":"forth","count":1},{"word":"lovely","count":1},{"word":"couple","count":1},{"word":"random","count":1},{"word":"fellow","count":1},{"word":"suggested","count":1},{"word":"hello","count":1},{"word":"gave","count":1},{"word":"try","count":1},{"word":"surprise","count":1},{"word":"understand","count":1},{"word":"eventually","count":1},{"word":"joined","count":1},{"word":"singing","count":1},{"word":"chill","count":1},{"word":"relaxing","count":1},{"word":"days","count":1},{"word":"good","count":1},{"word":"times","count":1},{"word":"never","count":1},{"word":"last","count":1},{"word":"happened","count":1},{"word":"afterwards","count":1},{"word":"outbreak","count":1},{"word":"every","count":1},{"word":"hungry","count":1},{"word":"tear","count":1},{"word":"everything","count":1},{"word":"shreds","count":1},{"word":"trying","count":1},{"word":"protect","count":1},{"word":"partner","count":1},{"word":"birds","count":1},{"word":"chewed","count":1},{"word":"alive","count":1},{"word":"rampant","count":1},{"word":"tds","count":1},{"word":"survived","count":1},{"word":"went","count":1},{"word":"mad","count":1},{"word":"later","count":1},{"word":"becoming","count":1},{"word":"today","count":1},{"word":"perhaps","count":1},{"word":"perspective","count":1},{"word":"time","count":1},{"word":"forever","count":1},{"word":"froze","count":1},{"word":"moment","count":1},{"word":"lived","count":1},{"word":"zombie","count":1},{"word":"denying","count":1},{"word":"attacking","count":1},{"word":"living","count":1},{"word":"approached","count":1},{"word":"bit","count":1},{"word":"early","count":1},{"word":"getting","count":1},{"word":"age","count":1},{"word":"practicing","count":1},{"word":"extra","count":1},{"word":"hours","count":1},{"word":"punishment","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"That's because you're doing it wrong, kiddo!","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"You little rascal... Ahem. What can this old man do for you, strangers?","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"Sure it can. It's something that was uniquely popular among us older generations. And all you need, get ready for it...","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"Is just an ordinary leaf.","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"Shush! Go away, you brat.","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"Find a leaf and pinch it together on one side like this... hold the other side close to your lips. Now blow along the edge to make sounds. You may even change the pitch—","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"Indeed. You can turn anything in the world into an instrument as long as you've got the music in you. If you put your heart into it, you can even use it to express your feelings.","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"When we were young, we would sit on the cliff after a long day of work and play some simple tunes with the leaves.","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"The Mourning Aix and the other bird TD rarely attacked anyone, and we'd watch the two always flying right beside each other off in the distance, back and forth like a lovely couple.","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"Some random fellow then suggested that we use the leaves to say hello. So we gave it a try, and to our surprise, not only did they understand us, they even eventually joined in singing to our tunes.","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"Boy, those were the chill and relaxing days.","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"Yep. Good times never last.","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"Yep. All because of what happened afterwards...","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"There was a TD Outbreak... Every TD out there was hungry for the sounds. Human or not human, they'd tear everything to shreds.","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"Trying to protect its partner, one of the \"birds\" were attacked and chewed up alive by rampant TDs. The one that survived went mad later because of it, becoming the Mourning Aix we all know today.","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"Perhaps from its perspective, time forever froze at that moment. From then on, it lived like a zombie, denying and attacking all living things that approached it.","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"A bit too early to be getting into these things for your age, don't you think, my boy?","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"Why you little... You're in for it now. You'll be practicing extra hours as punishment!","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002}]}